Ease fp ratio tests by a little bit.

RNG in python3 is different than python2.  Values returned are different
and this is enough to push the FP ratio test over the edge on python3,
even though there is no difference between the filters created by
python2 and python3.
hydra: Remove unneded imports
mmap_writer.c: allocate files with posix_fallocate

Create descriptor after getFilter call

This avoids descriptor files being left around when getFilter fails.

Delete tempfiles on object destruction

Anonymous filters, such as those in the tests, weren't deleted when the
BloomFilter object went away.  You can't read the name from outside the
module so you couldn't clean the file up even if you wanted to, nor know
what it was.  Instead, we use tempfile.NamedTemporaryFile to clean up
after ourselves.
